Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 剛才的男生很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激發母性本能的那一類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他制服 是星華的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 哪弄來的 黑龍 小美吉祥吊飾？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是我自製的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這麼手巧啊 幫我也做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到了學校要收好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天的便當是三層雙份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我參加了模仿秀節目一日遊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fender公司被CBS收購是1965年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:16.02,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fender:著名美產吉他公司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:29.92,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,145)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\c&HCCF7FD&}{\3c&H2B367B&}{\shad0}{\bord2}碓冰的對手？深谷陽向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷然實行部室等的大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹…幹嘛搞突然襲擊啊 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不突然 一直在叫你們打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己看看這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股奇臭已經到了肉眼都能看見的地步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 我們什麼都看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們自己身上就纏繞著這股奇臭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼啊 奇臭 好像很強 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之明天週六 全員大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定做不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想弄到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定連吃飯的時間都不給吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶慰問品來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做一下大掃除嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶飯糰之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村…你從哪冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見會長被圍住 慌忙之下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 多虧了你 他們才肯大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是仔細想想 那麼多人的慰問品…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按常理想不可能做得過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君也這麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰問品由學生會全體來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部室等的大掃除 是學生會接到的委託嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡全力做飯糰的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會因為一個飯糰就滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 最近你一直請假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 受了點小傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長也是 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好 我們走 幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 碓冰同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰勞品的話 你想要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是運動時的慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說我要粥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說粥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下週開始好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 週一再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟您商量下明天的大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給部員們做點慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.64,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動部慰問品分擔   購物組:幸村 槙村 澤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君 今天我會弄晚一點 你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長 請過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經成好朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長才是 已經成了他女朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就搞不清楚為什麼要隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和碓冰在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白癡嗎 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要和那種變態外星人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他女朋友 還去照顧他做粥給他喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 感覺出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…我欠他很多人情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法才去的 你別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:59.02,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然現在還有人會把情書塞鞋櫃裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你代我去吧 說是在2年級教室等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 還怕女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我扔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真交往不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌麻煩的話 就認真和一個女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就不會有這麼多人向你告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 會長自己好像還沒發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在才說這麼有趣的話啊 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在旁邊看著乾著急？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動真心太麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼小葵也混進來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又擅自穿我們的女僕裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經打烊了 有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來該穗香站前面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國中生趕緊回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們也準備回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如大家一起吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗香能去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好地方推薦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是廚房姊妹花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天飯食點餐比預計的少 剩了些米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用剩的飯做了飯糰 大家請嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在女僕拿鐵吃飯好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真省錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美在的話 就讓她拿回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我成形 我要三角形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 有雜念…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣捏應該能成形…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習下捏飯糰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再浪費糧食了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何 把紙巾撕碎搓圓捏緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是紗奈 貧窮生智慧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這下能放手大幹一場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能放心捏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始做慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 你臉色很難看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 完全OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 早上已經能捏出形狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自分好工作開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 幫忙的人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我閒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:06.61,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(730,150)}只\N是\N捏\N飯\N糰\N的\N話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰學長不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 今天沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村學長 你怎麼看會長和碓冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是強人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想問什麼 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 兩人的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭檔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.18,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(56,170)}{\frz12}捏\N完\N一\N個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習運動樣樣精通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像人種不同似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺他們的世界無法企及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我 總是讓會長幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像碓冰一樣無所不通的話 就能幫上會長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村學長喜歡會長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是交往那種喜歡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 幸村 還有閒心聊天 快給我做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.21,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(406,170)}垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近蔬菜吃得少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了 做得非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裡怎麼有球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是飯糰哦 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是飯糰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我吃給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧 是飯糰吧 鹹味的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我怎麼聽到了不可思議的咀嚼聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你幻聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的慰勞品還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃除好好做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 裡面混有不明球狀物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ABESHI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真夠膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動部的人 勇氣可嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:54.09,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:54.84,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先收拾殘局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.44,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪唧 啪唧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美球到手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳家寶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有光澤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳家寶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要珍藏一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…有好好打掃完再走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打掃怎麼不把這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:36.83,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼有種乾年糕的嚼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真夠慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵練習了半天就這成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次做的粥還算好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成這樣 那傢伙也不肯吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做出這種神器的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然贏不了鮎澤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等 我把包拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼兩心相悅 卻無法完全表達呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說那種謊言 不想進一步發展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在自言自語什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那個飯糰到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是見鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你為什麼每次都神出鬼沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我出現得很平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我又不是從天而降的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人會從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好還好 我居然弄掉了寶貴的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚼嚼嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不小心 不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是轉學生 深谷陽向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地出身 出於某些原因在九州住了十年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜂蜜檸檬味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想要的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你好了 你不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好人吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深谷 不許在班會上吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.58,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,20)}同 情 視 線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傷心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 剛來就慣著他怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規矩不能亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫深谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把糖收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.27,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人家弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你哭什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.54,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼啊 魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這邊是體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.30,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚼嚼嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要我提醒幾次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了不准邊走邊吃東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛 我餓的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要也得要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 抱歉打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會議上分發的資料麻煩你核對下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包邊暫時放我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 魔鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真是高中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想和你打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡修正 還有剛才說的地方添加內容 其餘都OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按人數影印裝訂整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都在陪著轉學生啊 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不理我 人家好寂寞的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看出你想讓我理的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根本沒見你人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 但我一直看著會長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 不愧是變態跟蹤狂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮎澤也看到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有看我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉學生出事了 好像被男生圍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情況很危險 就先來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊嗎 你們在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 剛才還一副要開戰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在來猜猜我手上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味棒CHESS味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厲害 陽向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒開袋都能聞出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你怎麼吃都吃不胖耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我以前是個大胖子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是上小學的時候 爸媽出車禍去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就搬去了九州爺爺那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡窮得連個粗點店都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是啃蔬菜 自然就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我爺爺說 有我在幾塊田都不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回以前住的這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身世好像還蠻沉重的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人住？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學費呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠老爸他們留的錢支撐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苦了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為只是個貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意輕鬆面對慘痛的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘痛？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了找初戀的女孩子才回來這城市的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到能再見到她 就興奮得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才你說被爺爺趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 最後爺爺說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「開個玩笑 你還是留在這吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挽留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.65,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,300)}身無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 你要掛點的時候我再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就是一心為了見那個女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今後為了找她會變得很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是那麼溫柔開朗會照顧人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 她就好比草原上的一朵惹人憐惜的花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好想讓你再餵我吃甜甜的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我哦 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 深谷 你確定那個女孩在這所學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡找她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和她約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一輩子跟著美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人跟著女人 你也太靠不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是這樣約定的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 美咲…這名字好像在哪聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 很危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿小陽你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後別隨便爬到樹上去 要好好跟著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你 一輩子都跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:09.62,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥豬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 他說的美咲不會就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 通常不是應該早就發覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了這麼多話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽向…（訓讀）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOUKOU？（音讀）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候 有個男生外號叫YOUKOU
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字的漢字可以用那種讀法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.63,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(735,50)}{\frz10}Y\NO\NU\NK\NO\NU
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.63,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(179,50)}{\frz-30}今\N天\N又\N在\N吃\N啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是很能吃 長得很胖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要找的初戀女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.89,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(155,10)}從小就是好管閒事的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.89,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,10)}小陽 你一個人沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那時候美咲和陽向君交往過？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歡樂的情節發展
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 陽向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 整個學校盡收眼底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 美咲 快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨到家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有心思笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下來 深谷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡就不會被笨蛋魔鬼打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再掉下來我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不下來 糖和麵包邊全部沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮎澤美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我已經不是從前的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.54,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,150)}{\fs40}真的假的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到轉學生深谷居然是那個小陽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 碓冰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 油炸麵包邊裹糖很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吃也不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麵包邊你從哪拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是特地跑來讓我沒收的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想美咲搭理他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 靜子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 加上轉學生 下集是林間夏令營哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是要去山間寺廟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:10.81,biaoti2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(730,355)}{\c&H509EF5&}{\fad(300,0)}林間夏令營躲貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:06.89,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}どうか Please！can you keep my secret
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.90,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}キラキラと輝くミラー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:29.78,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}私はどんなふうに映っているの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.44,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}ホラホラと手招く未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:39.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}これからどんなコトが起こるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:50.68,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}目に見えているモノがスベテではないから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.43,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}無我夢中でThat's ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.07,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}迷わないで I wanna TRY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:01:00.98,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}自分のキモチにまっすぐでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.87,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}だけど１つや２つくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.33,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}誰にもバレたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:11.34,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}ナイショってあるものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:17.17,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}胸がちょっと痛む　my secret
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:06.89,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}求求你 Please！can you keep my secret
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.90,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}閃爍光芒的鏡子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:29.78,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}我究竟是什麼模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.44,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}快樂招手的未來裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:39.60,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}又將會發生些什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:50.68,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}因為所見並非一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.43,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}心醉神迷 That's ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.07,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}不要迷茫 I wanna TRY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:01:00.98,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}想真心面對自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.87,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}但哪怕只是一兩件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.33,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}也不想透露給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:11.34,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}因為那是我心中的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:17.17,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}心口隱隱作痛　my secret
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:18.40,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}きっとまた会える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:32.53,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}その目に映るものすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.89,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}幻に見えませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:39.57,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}絡み合い解けてゆく中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:44.72,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}君は何を感じてるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:48.19,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}見てごらん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:54.52,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}欲張っても繋がった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:23:00.55,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}その理由を悲しみから縋ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:04.24,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}そんなものでいいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:10.54,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}飾らないまま　迎える美しさよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:14.88,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}いつの日にか分かろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.78,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}たとえ何処に居たとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:25.47,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}きっとまた会える
